    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's looking for a new home! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in great shape, perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures. It runs smoothly and has been well-loved, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic car that's ready to hit the road immediately. Come by and take it for a test drive\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
